5760 
5761         // @private
5762         var calculateNormals = function(positions, indices) {
5763             var nvecs = new Array(positions.length);
5764 
5765             for (var i = 0; i < indices.length; i++) {
5766                 var j0 = indices[i][0];
5767                 var j1 = indices[i][1];
5768                 var j2 = indices[i][2];
5769 
5770                 var v1 = positions[j0];
5771                 var v2 = positions[j1];
5772                 var v3 = positions[j2];
5773 
5774                 var va = SceneJS_math_subVec4(v2, v1);
5775                 var vb = SceneJS_math_subVec4(v3, v1);
5776 
5777                 var n = SceneJS_math_normalizeVec4(SceneJS_math_cross3Vec4(va, vb));
5778 
5779                 if (!nvecs[j0]) nvecs[j0] = [];
5780                 if (!nvecs[j1]) nvecs[j1] = [];
5781                 if (!nvecs[j2]) nvecs[j2] = [];
5782 
5783                 nvecs[j0].push(n);
5784                 nvecs[j1].push(n);
5785                 nvecs[j2].push(n);
5786             }
5787 
5788             var normals = new Array(positions.length);
5789 
5790             // now go through and average out everything
5791             for (var i = 0; i < nvecs.length; i++) {
5792                 var count = nvecs[i].length;
5793                 var x = 0;
5794                 var y = 0;
5795                 var z = 0;
5796                 for (var j = 0; j < count; j++) {
5797                     x += nvecs[i][j][0];
5798                     y += nvecs[i][j][1];
5799                     z += nvecs[i][j][2];
5800                 }
5801                 normals[i] = [x / count, y / count, z / count];
5802             }
5803             return normals;
5804         };
5805 
5806         // @private
5807         var flatten = function (ar, numPerElement) {
5808             var result = [];
5809             for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++) {
5810                 if (numPerElement && ar[i].length != numPerElement)
5811                     throw new SceneJS.exceptions.InvalidGeometryConfigException("Bad geometry array element");
5812                 for (var j = 0; j < ar[i].length; j++)
5813                     result.push(ar[i][j]);
5814             }
5815             return result;
5816         };
5817         return {
5818             primitive:"triangles",
5819             positions: flatten(positions, 3),
5820             indices:flatten(indices, 3),
5821             normals:flatten(calculateNormals(positions, indices), 3)
5822         };
5823     };
5824 };

5826 SceneJS._utils.inherit(SceneJS.objects.Teapot, SceneJS.Geometry);

5829  */
5830 SceneJS.objects.teapot = function() {
5831     return new SceneJS.objects.Teapot();
